## ğŸ“¦ Installation

1. **Clone the Repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/kivy-calculator.git
   cd kivy-calculator
   ```

2. **Install Dependencies**
   ```bash
   pip install kivy
   ```

3. **Run the App**
   ```bash
   python main.py
   ```

